Package com.xin.popgen.infos

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Info
    Interface Info defines common methods for reading files in SeleDiff.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CountInfo
    Class CountInfo is used for counting alleles and obtaining SNP information from a .count file.
    GenoInfo
    Class GenoInfo is used for counting alleles from genotype file in EIGENSTRAT format.
    IndInfo
    Class IndInfo stores the sample information, including: population IDs, individual IDs, population numbers and individual numbers.
    PopInfo
    Created by deep on 18-7-27.
    PopVarInfo
    Class PopVarInfo stores variances of Omega between populations.
    SnpInfo
    Class SnpInfo stores the number of SNPs in the sample.
    TimeInfo
    Class TimeInfo stores the information of divergence times for population pairs in the sample.
    VcfInfo
    Class VcfInfo is used for counting alleles and obtaining SNP information from a VCF file.
